{
  "texts": [
    "We require the LLMs to simulate a doctor and provide responses based on various patient inquiries.",
    "Each junior annotator is assigned to independently compare the responses from public LLMs and those from the leading commercial LLMs, i.e., Claude-2, GPT-3.5-turbo, and GPT-4, in terms of the perceived quality of the responses.",
    "It includes faithfulness, comprehensiveness, generalizability, and robustness.",
    "The senior annotator re-evaluates the cases that are difficult for junior annotators to decide.",
    "The annotators are of which model generates these reports."
  ]
}